title: Saints.Row.IV.Repack.R.G. Catalyst
description:
Saints.Row.IV.Repack.R.G. Catalyst

Year: 2013 
Publication Type: Repack 
Tablet: enclosing RELOADED 
Language: English, German, Spanish, Italian, French, Polish 
Sound language: English 

Description: 

Using a huge arsenal of weapons and incredible super-powers, the President 
of the United States of America must save the Earth from alien invaders, 
Lord Zinyakov. You will most insane "open world" ever created. 

An epic end the game that changed all the rules! "Saints" were a long way 
from shooting galleries to the White House, but the invasion on Earth, 
and only you can save the world from Lord Zinyakov and his alien empire. 
Together with his mates, armed with an arsenal of super abilities and 
strange guns, you have to save the world in this very wild and 
incredible gaming universe 

Features repack: 

Do not recoded / no cut 
Includes DLC: 
"Brady Games Pack", 
"Commander-In-Chief Pack",
"Hillbilly Pack", 
"Presidential Pack",
"Team Fortress 2 Pack", 
"The Rectifier", 
"Volition Comics Pack", 
"The Executive Privilege Pack " 

Installation time ~ 10 min. 


System requirements: 

Operating system: Windows Vista SP2  Windows 7 SP1  Windows 8 
Processor: Intel Core 2 Quad processor with a clock speed of 2.4 GHz 
Memory: 4 GB 
Video Card: 1 GB of video memory (NVIDIA GeForce GTX 260 / ATI Radeon HD 5800) 
Sound Card: DirectX 9.0c compatible 
Free hard drive space: 9 GB
